    "body": "This is a follow-up to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/33929.\r\n\r\nUsing `BOOST_FAIL` macros in `mock_process` triggers Windows CRT memory leak dumps during \"Debug\" builds, which [breaks](https://github.com/hebasto/bitcoin-core-nightly/actions/runs/22791729012/job/66119635880) `system_tests`. This PR explicitly disables memory leak detection when invoking `mock_process`.",
