      "message": "test: Disable memory leak detection in `mock_process`\n\nUsing `BOOST_FAIL` macros in `mock_process` triggers Windows CRT memory\nleak dumps during \"Debug\" builds, which breaks `system_tests`. This\nchange explicitly disables memory leak detection when invoking\n`mock_process`.",
